We hope you’re enjoying Badoo! All our updates are designed to improve reliability, speed and the general, overall usefulness of our app. For new features and other exciting changes, we’ll let you know directly!

Badoo Live
Drumroll please… Introducing Badoo Live! Share your everyday moments and show off your talents with new live streams, a whole new way to meet and connect with people on Badoo.

Of course, we added a bunch of bug fixes and enhancements, too – but we know what we’re most excited about!
